<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Meet the Developers - Fitsane</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6e8efb, #a777e3);
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            width: 350px;
            height: 500px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            transition: transform 0.4s ease-in-out;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .card img {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 5px solid #a777e3 ;
            background: white;
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto 15px;
        }
        .card h3 {
            margin: 10px 0 5px;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: black;
        }
        .card p {
            color: black;
            margin: 5px 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            padding: 0 10px;
        }
        .card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            z-index: 10;
        }
        .social-icons {
            margin-top: 15px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .social-icons a {
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .social-icons img {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            color: white;
        }

        .role{
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #a777e3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Meet the Developers</h1>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <img src="/images/imageme.jpg" alt="Pranay Pillay">
            <h3>Pranay Pillay</h3>
            <p><span class="role">Lead Developer</span></p>
            <p>Lead full-stack Developer who built the backend using Node.js, Express.js, EJS, MongoDB, and various validation features. Also designed the frontend including homepage, register, login, BMI calculator, and review pages.</p>
            <div class="social-icons">
                <a href="#"><img src="/images/instagram.png" alt="Instagram"></a>
                <a href="#"><img src="/images/twitter.png" alt="Twitter"></a>
                <a href="#"><img src="/images/facebook.png" alt="Facebook"></a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img src="/images/imagaeabhi.jpg" alt="Abhishek Sagar">
            <h3>Abhishek Sagar</h3>
            <p><span class="role">Frontend Developer</span></p>
            <p>Frontend Developer who worked on and designed the landing page and three workout pages for different user preferences using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Also contributed to documentation.</p>
            <div class="social-icons">
                <a href="#"><img src="/images/instagram.png" alt="Instagram"></a>
                <a href="#"><img src="/images/twitter.png" alt="Twitter"></a>
                <a href="#"><img src="/images/facebook.png" alt="Facebook"></a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img src="/images/imagetej.jpg" alt="Tejas Sooryavanshi">
            <h3>Tejas Suryawanshi</h3>
            <p><span class="role">Frontend Developer</span></p>
            <p>Frontend Developer who worked on the nutrition pages, developing three nutrition plans tailored to different body types using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Also prepared detailed nutrition diet plans.</p>
            <div class="social-icons">
                <a href="#"><img src="/images/instagram.png" alt="Instagram"></a>
                <a href="#"><img src="/images/twitter.png" alt="Twitter"></a>
                <a href="#"><img src="/images/facebook.png" alt="Facebook"></a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <img src="/images/imgsajid.jpg" alt="Abhishek Sagar">
            <h3>Mohammad sajid shaikh</h3>
            <p><span class="role">Frontend Developer</span></p>
            <p>Frontend Developer who worked on and designed the landing page and three workout pages for different user preferences using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Also contributed to documentation.</p>
            <div class="social-icons">
                <a href="#"><img src="/images/instagram.png" alt="Instagram"></a>
                <a href="#"><img src="/images/twitter.png" alt="Twitter"></a>
                <a href="#"><img src="/images/facebook.png" alt="Facebook"></a>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</body>
</html>
